Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.59,0:00:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音紋對照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.62,0:00:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往一點鐘方向集中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.90,0:00:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊，是EXILE嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.11,0:00:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是EXILE的音紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.81,0:00:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是度西斯艦的殘骸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.82,0:01:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽音員集中注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.17,0:01:14.60,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.67,0:01:18.23,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.31,0:01:25.51,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.58,0:01:32.51,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.59,0:01:38.82,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲 飛向雲海的彼端 \N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony  雲の海の向こうに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.89,0:01:46.80,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.14,0:02:01.38,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.45,0:02:15.85,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.93,0:02:26.33,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.89,0:02:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}大風暴區\NGrand Stream
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後一批了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們向烏爾班號\N借來了錨型魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.44,0:03:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要用這個來捕獲EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標的形狀呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.88,0:03:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它四周包圍著一層繭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.98,0:03:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE的防禦系統非常強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須極端小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒隊由3，4號機擔任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主力部隊由1號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，艾麗絲蒂亞\N妳們擔任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.10,0:03:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.33,0:03:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5號機，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領航員……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧，由你來擔任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.87,0:03:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有戴芬妮在的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.85,0:03:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧，求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.59,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.49,0:04:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到好大的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.99,0:05:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是烏爾班號的音響魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，迪奧的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在無音航行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是太吵會被罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.00,0:05:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才布萊恩叔叔\N有教我怎麼作蛋糕……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.52,0:05:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備發射下一枚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.84,0:05:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.81,0:05:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.21,0:05:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搜索區還剩下五個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝下一個搜索區移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.09,0:06:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音響魚雷還剩幾枚可以發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,餘彈三枚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定可以找到的，陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.78,0:06:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要來一局嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那個心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日週是到明天結束嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要過了明天\N額頭上的印記也會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.89,0:06:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望可以逃得過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.12,0:06:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向安那托勒皇帝建議\N由迪奧殿下出戰是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.16,0:06:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好是做點事情\N才能讓心情放鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主客還沒到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希卡達前去迎駕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.08,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，那我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.23,0:07:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組件開始脫離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的基爾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.41,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊急著陸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到鳥肉其實還滿好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真野蠻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是這樣鼻毛才會長那麼長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.12,0:07:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，怎麼這樣惡搞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才活下來的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度我們是不會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家可都是身經百戰的勇士呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.21,0:08:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今我方已經有五艘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.31,0:08:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴方也已經有兩艘\N因組件的強制脫離而沈沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.98,0:08:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方建議\N立刻執行組件奪取計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.62,0:08:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰日已決定為\N山羊月13日的04：00
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.03,0:08:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁著基爾特宣誓典禮時進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.93,0:08:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是要我眼睜睜的看著\N我們的船艦一艘艘地沈沒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.27,0:08:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的基爾特人\N都會去參加宣誓典禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時只要趁虛而入就可以打贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就等吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.55,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧，你跟我來一下好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一點，快點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等……等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離到達目標地點還有珨十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.87,0:09:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與烏爾班號距離三百
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.84,0:09:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風很大，當心撞上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.91,0:09:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.58,0:09:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請開始準備作聲納搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快來，這邊這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一片黑漆漆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是幹嘛……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.89,0:09:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.86,0:09:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來基爾特也會過生日啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我珍藏的酒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧他會喝酒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們要喝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，這是你的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不喜歡基爾特人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你已經是我們的夥伴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.78,0:09:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.95,0:09:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這代表的是一份心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.12,0:09:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是很頂級的水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要珍惜著點喝唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.59,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是舊東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.69,0:09:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有蛋糕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧你吃吃看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.48,0:10:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.65,0:10:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢，好好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.49,0:10:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也分給我們一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.26,0:10:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來喝，來喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.33,0:10:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家看起來都好開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.93,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.89,0:10:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們都是\N這樣來慶祝生日週的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人羨慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.84,0:10:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你討厭花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭的並不是花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，開心一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是宴會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.81,0:10:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輪班前就給它鬧個夠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始進行聲納搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入無音航行狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.12,0:11:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我們就來安靜的鬧個夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.49,0:11:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射音響魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.23,0:11:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我現身吧，EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.21,0:11:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過生日喔，好開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.61,0:11:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我作的生日歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.51,0:11:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生然後回歸大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.73,0:11:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.16,0:11:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相對方位，負15
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.20,0:11:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離一萬八千
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.53,0:11:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在接近當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.67,0:11:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力全開，左舵15
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快做音紋對照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驅動音吻合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是有生命似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.16,0:12:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1，2，3，唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.80,0:12:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過生日喔，好開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.97,0:12:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生然後回歸大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.91,0:12:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝福你，祝福你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂\N祝你生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.95,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這種生日週的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.38,0:12:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管再過多少次我都願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無音航行解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.55,0:12:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始要進入捕獲EXILE行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.02,0:12:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各人員進行準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等了好久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.09,0:12:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，一口氣給它搞定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，不要在那裡磨蹭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5號機的領航員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.93,0:12:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不快給我上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被人命令了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候我該怎麼回答才好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.24,0:13:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要回答瞭解，迪奧殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.08,0:13:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼……瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.69,0:13:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮總帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧殿下……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.09,0:13:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他人似乎在侵入大風暴區的\N那艘未登錄的船艦上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上去處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屬下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.87,0:13:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉搞不好會從中阻撓喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.90,0:13:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候就……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真殘忍，希卡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虧你們還是兄弟呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.08,0:13:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到真的有EXILE的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果它到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.69,0:13:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說是終極的超巨型戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.89,0:13:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是聽說那是個比空中船塢\N還要來得更大的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.26,0:13:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有人說那是創造了\N這個世界的神所沈睡的棺材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.20,0:14:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦開啟了它世界就會毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴族少爺應該知道些什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情形我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.94,0:14:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為戴芬妮叫我不可以靠近它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊薩，不要在那裡發呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不快幫1號機的引擎熱機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.71,0:14:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興能再跟妳一起飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.75,0:14:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的性命就交給妳囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.22,0:14:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士也要飛在這片天空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像以前的你一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.76,0:14:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把艾兒‧薇絲帶來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.00,0:14:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小地方就不用管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.24,0:14:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要特別注意馬力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣，大概像這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.91,0:14:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.11,0:14:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一下子就會用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.28,0:14:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.14,0:14:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那個基爾特人\N怎麼一副很臭屁的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.21,0:14:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就照迪奧所說的去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.65,0:14:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟大風暴區他比較熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要活著回來哦，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.49,0:14:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很遺憾我不能跟你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了將來可以和拉薇妳一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力去好好飛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說好好飛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你抱著這麼天真的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.83,0:15:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當心會被颳跑哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.54,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說\N那可是時速120節的強風啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,120節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.31,0:15:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果一個弄不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.24,0:15:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有抓著纜繩\N被甩來甩去的份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.61,0:15:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會有事吧，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要照我說的去做就安啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.35,0:15:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.72,0:15:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要代替我好好的領航哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.39,0:15:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒隊，可以起飛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去3號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請立刻緊急回收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.31,0:15:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，不要太勉強自己哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看他那樣\N克勞士的本事可是很厲害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒‧薇絲，妳跟我來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事情要拜託妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.55,0:16:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事只有妳辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.62,0:16:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我辦得到的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5號機，纜繩安裝完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.97,0:16:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1號機，纜繩安裝完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.64,0:16:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1號機，5號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以起飛了\N瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.95,0:16:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.98,0:16:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了，各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是大風暴區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.00,0:16:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用基爾特的機器\N可絕對沒辦法嘗到這種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.34,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能逆風而行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要乘著氣流走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5號機，報告狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相對方位15度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以135節速度飛行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纜繩打結了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.59,0:17:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順著氣流向右旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.32,0:17:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼讚透了，衝啊\N我們可不是來玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.06,0:17:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用心在任務上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.43,0:17:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.86,0:17:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,視界500
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.90,0:17:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標方位335
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏位角負4
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.83,0:17:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是4號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已目測到疑似EXILE的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.60,0:17:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請作確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.34,0:17:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認相對位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.14,0:17:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是EXILE沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4號機\N在後續部隊到達前請待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.65,0:17:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5號機，目標在十點鐘方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在拉開距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.85,0:17:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果把風考慮進去\N這樣就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.42,0:17:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要囉哩囉嗦的很煩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到捕獲EXILE之後\N就把關鍵謎詩……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纜繩剩餘長度500
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.44,0:17:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請本艦向目標靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.27,0:17:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舵15，第四航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也請告知烏爾班號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.84,0:18:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.01,0:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.65,0:18:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.25,0:18:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不跟著他一起去沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓他做自己想做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.59,0:18:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來應該是可以順利過關吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.26,0:18:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，一副鬱鬱寡歡的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.98,0:18:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.04,0:18:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學得真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE應該很近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.58,0:18:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請小心，前方有亂流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已目測到4號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也確認到EXILE的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.76,0:18:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊也到達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.49,0:18:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請開始執行任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.89,0:18:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.50,0:18:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.93,0:18:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4號機，現在開始要接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.60,0:19:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.64,0:19:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，被彈開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.52,0:19:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去4號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.95,0:19:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是EXILE的防衛反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.89,0:19:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.06,0:19:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經被它鎖定為目標了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.42,0:19:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.17,0:19:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來抓我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在哪是玩耍的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.00,0:19:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是沒有辦法射進它的表面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.97,0:19:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.41,0:19:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看，只要射進\N那些方塊的下面不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.61,0:19:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看有空隙不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.01,0:19:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空隙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.55,0:19:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1號機開始接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗絲，準備好魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.83,0:19:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.73,0:20:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.83,0:20:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，妳沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.37,0:20:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1號機，請速返航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我至少還可以進行支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用擔心我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.51,0:20:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要回去也很辛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.54,0:20:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.71,0:20:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.98,0:20:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1號機這就返航了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.65,0:20:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交給我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.15,0:20:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧，把機槍的彈藥裝填好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.36,0:20:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.89,0:20:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5號機，要開始接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.13,0:20:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要去囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機體撐得住嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安啦安啦，衝吧衝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.77,0:20:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.28,0:20:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧，魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.75,0:20:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧，馬力開到最大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.39,0:21:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.06,0:21:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我的厲害了吧，戴芬妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.03,0:21:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5號機這就直接返航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.23,0:21:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有他們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.34,0:21:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.74,0:21:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.68,0:21:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲板人員，請射出錨索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.84,0:21:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.75,0:21:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要跟妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.95,0:21:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.49,0:21:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是關鍵謎詩\N把它和貨物一起帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.76,0:21:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.39,0:21:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一來我欠馬留司的人情\N也算還完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就讓我做我想做的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.36,0:21:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳轉到烏爾班號上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.63,0:21:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會離開銀之戰艦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.27,0:21:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.64,0:21:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我是不會再接受\N任何皇帝的指令的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.51,0:21:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也包括副艦長的建言嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.31,0:21:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.28,0:22:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將EXILE接上纜繩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.52,0:22:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把絞盤捲起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.43,0:22:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過生日喔，好開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.43,0:22:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生然後回歸大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.55,0:22:39.99,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.52,0:22:46.55,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.63,0:22:51.86,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.93,0:22:57.67,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.74,0:23:03.37,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你奮不顧身的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.44,0:23:12.22,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.29,0:23:18.16,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.22,0:23:23.96,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.03,0:23:29.80,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.87,0:23:35.67,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.74,0:23:48.25,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.12,0:23:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回預告）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.69,0:23:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過生日喔，好開心\N拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.46,0:23:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生然後回歸大地\N艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.87,0:24:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是發生了什麼事\N銀之戰艦是幽靈船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.07,0:24:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉也不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.87,0:24:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和英麥曼兩人獨自在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.98,0:24:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最後流亡 第21話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.58,0:24:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧的城堡\NRook Dio
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.78,0:24:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你遲遲不回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.98,0:24:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只好去來接你了
